1. Checking git version : git --version

2. Setting Username: git config --global user.name "Harshal Dhongadi"
2.1. For checking username: git config --global user.name

3. Setting EmailId: git config --global user.email "harshal.dhongadi@anmsoft.com"
3.1. For checking userEmail: git config --global user.email

4. Making changes in the main config file of git: git config --global --edit
4.1 After making changes : press escape and then type ":wq"


